'''Garham's-on-the-Downstream''' was a bar in the nation of [[Cartann]], on the planet [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. It boasted expensive columns of stone, curtained booths, excellent service, decent [[Alcohol/Legends|drinks]] and provided privacy for its customers. While in the bar, [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] encountered [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Teren Rogriss]] during their diplomatic [[Mission to Adumar|mission]] to Adumar.<ref name="SOR">''[[X-Wing: Starfighters of Adumar]]''</ref>

